original: Once, a large turkey had aspirations to race against his companions. Together, they ventured to the fair for a friendly competition. Impressively, the turkey emerged victorious, showcasing his speed and agility. His friends celebrated his triumph, and together, they enjoyed a joyous time at the fair. And so, their day of camaraderie came to an end.
